ricans\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I saw myself as an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing it 'at home' is the opportunity of a lifetime.\\\"\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For years, Spain and Argentina were the biggest challenges to Team USA on the international stage.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999986806996793, \"rank\": 1.2101718139963596e-06, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999958636707614, \"rank\": 2.1816412641555493e-06, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.51303438922637e-13, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_ph